Packages that use com.qualcomm.toq.smartwatch.api.v1.deckofcards.card
com.qualcomm.toq.smartwatch.api.v1.deckofcards Contains deck of cards applet and notification model classes, exceptions and general classes. 
com.qualcomm.toq.smartwatch.api.v1.deckofcards.card Contains the classes for creating a specialisation of a Card or list of Cards for use with a DeckOfCards or ToqNotification. 
com.qualcomm.toq.smartwatch.api.v1.deckofcards.remote Contains the classes required to interact with the remote Toq app's API service.
